`f_j` a level-1 weight-90 form with rational coefficients in `(E₄, E₆)`.

The Sturm bound for weight 90 is `⌊90/12⌋ + 1 = 8`. After certifying agreement
on the first 8 q-coefficients, `ModularForm.eq_of_sturm_bound` lets us conclude that any
form with the same coefficients equals our explicit `lmfdb_1_90_a_orbit`.

